---
layout: page
title: Games
description: Games I've played
---
<p>I own {{ games.keysByPlaytime | length }} games with total playtime of {{ games.totalPlaytime }} hours. See my <a href="/tags/gaming">gaming related posts</a>.</p>
<h2>Recently Played</h2>
<div class="grid gap-x-4 gap-y-6 mx-auto px-0 mt-4 grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3">
    {% for gameKey in games.keysByLastPlayed %}
        {% set game = games.games[gameKey] %}
        <div class="justify-start items-center last-of-type:hidden sm:!flex">
            <a class="my-0" href="{{ game.bricksetUrl }}">
                <img src="{{ game.headerImage.src }}" alt="{{ game.name }}" class="w-full">
                <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-center">{{ game.name }}</p>
            </a>
            <p class="secondary my-0">
                {{ game.playtime.hours}}h
            </p>
        </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>
<h2>All Games</h2>
<div class="grid gap-x-4 gap-y-6 mx-auto px-0 mt-4 grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3">
    {% for gameKey in games.keysByPlaytime %}
        {% set game = games.games[gameKey] %}
        <div class="justify-start items-center">
            <a class="my-0" href="{{ game.bricksetUrl }}">
                <img src="{{ game.headerImage.src }}" alt="{{ game.name }}" class="w-full">
                <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-center">{{ game.name }}</p>
            </a>
            <p class="secondary my-0">
                {{ game.playtime.hours}}h
            </p>
        </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>